为了给孩子们发新书，上海的老师和学校拼了。
In order to distribute new books to the children, the teachers in Shanghai spell with the school.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 韩晓蓉上海市宝山区美罗家园第一小学的家长们自觉戴上口罩，彼此相隔一米以上排队。
Pai journalist Han Xiaolong Shanghai Baoshan City Meiluojiayuan primary school parents consciously wear masks, between each other more than a meter apart in line.
均为受访者供图把教材安全送到孩子手中，上海的教师和家长配合默契。
All of the respondents were provided with materials for safe delivery to their children, and teachers and parents in Shanghai worked well together.
在上海市宝山区美罗家园第一小学，所有分发教材的教师保持一米以上的距离，各班家长们自觉戴上口罩，同样每人间隔一米。
In Shanghai Baoshan District Meiluojiayuan Primary School No. 1, all teachers of the distribution of textbooks maintain a distance of more than one meter, the class parents consciously wear masks, also one meter apart.
受疫情影响，上海140多万中小学生从3月2日起开始在线教育，上海市教委要求，在发放电子教材的基础上，各学校坚持“消毒防控、自愿预约、分散领取、确保安全”原则，陆续开展纸质教材的发放工作，确保学生3月2日在线学习开展前，人手一套纸质教材或电子教材。
Affected by the epidemic, more than 1.4 million primary and secondary school students in Shanghai began online education on March 2. The Shanghai Education Commission has asked schools to adhere to the principles of disinfection prevention and control, voluntary appointment, decentralized collection and ensuring safety on the basis of electronic textbooks.
教师分发教材家长间隔一米排队领教材上海市宝山区美罗家园第一小学（简称“美罗一小”）相关负责人介绍，根据上海市教委和宝山区教育局的相关要求，学校在征询家长意见的基础上，制定了灵活的纸质教材发放方案。
According to the request of Shanghai Municipal Education Commission and Baoshan District Education Bureau, the school has formulated a flexible distribution plan for paper-based textbooks based on consultation with parents.
由学校提前做好预约登记工作，合理安排领取时段、领取地点和领取方式。
Schools should book appointments well in advance and arrange the collection time, place and method of collection reasonably.
纸质教材的领取方式包括到校领取和快递寄送。
Collection of paper textbooks includes collection at school and delivery by courier.
根据学校前期意见征询单数据显示，大部分家长自愿到校领取教材。
According to the data from the consultation sheet, most parents come to school voluntarily to receive textbooks.
为此，美罗一小分批利用两到三天的时间，为全校学生的教材进行消毒、分装打包。
To this end, Merlot uses small batches of two to three days to disinfect, pack and pack the entire school's teaching materials.
学校高度重视教材分发环节的卫生防控措施，教师们进校门先测体温、填写登记表，再戴上手套、口罩，全副武装进行分书行动。
The school attaches great importance to the preventive and control measures in the distribution of textbooks. Teachers take temperature tests, fill in registration forms, put on gloves, face masks, and carry out book-splitting operations with full equipment.
从分书到清点，再到最后的打包，所有教师保持一米以上的距离，确保分发环节中相对的独立性，避免交叉环节。
From the split book to the count to the final packaging, all teachers maintain a distance of more than one metre, ensuring relative independence in the distribution chain and avoiding cross-links.
此外，美罗一小还安排了后勤工作人员对教材进行最后的消毒处理。
In addition, a small Merlot logistics staff to arrange for the final disinfection of teaching materials.
学校还提前设计了家长领取教材的路线图和流程规划。
Roadmaps and process planning for parents' access to educational materials have also been designed in advance.
从早上8点到下午4点，每班预留一个小时分发教材，各班家长们自觉戴上口罩，彼此间隔一米以上排队，教材发放领取工作有序开展。
From 8 a.m. to 4 p.m., one hour is set aside for each class to distribute teaching materials. Classes' parents are self-conscious about wearing masks and queuing more than one metre apart.
同样，行知中学也采取分年级、分班级、分时段、免接触原则，安排教职员工“一人一包”完成纸质教材分发，做好教材、场地等清洁消毒工作。
Similarly, Xingzhi Middle School adopts the principles of grade, class, time and contact-free, and arranges the staff to distribute paper textbooks "one by one," and does a good job of cleaning and disinfecting materials, sites and so on.
在教材领取现场，学校在地面上黏贴1米间隔排队的黄色警示条，入口处黑板上放置醒目的发放流程示意图，告知家长材料领取流程。
At the scene of the collection, the school pasted yellow warning signs on the ground, lined up at 1m intervals, and bold distribution flow charts were placed on the entrance blackboard to inform parents about the material collection process.
在学校引导下，每位家长间隔一米有序排队，在进入登记处后由班主任查验学生证后，自提教材。
Under the guidance of the school, each parent is lined up one meter apart, and after entering the registration office, the head teacher checks the student card and presents his own teaching materials.
此外，学校还设有教材清点处，每人一桌，贴有教材清单和放置免洗消毒液供家长使用。
In addition, the school has an inventory of teaching materials, a table for each person, a list of teaching materials and a disinfectant for parents.
在闵行区莘松中学，教师们分拣打包之快，让人咋舌，网上热传的一段魔性“灵魂分拣员”视频让教师们再度成为网红，莘松中学的教师们不断规范操作流程，逐步提高工作效率，很快完成了两个校区近3000名学生课本的分拣打包。
In Min Hang District Cynthson Middle School, teachers sorted and packed up quickly, and the online heat of a demon "soul sorter" video made teachers become net red once again. Teachers at Cynthson Middle School kept standardizing the process and gradually improving work efficiency, and quickly finished sorting and packaging nearly 3,000 textbooks for the two campuses.
经过这样的“魔鬼训练”，教师们笑称，已经熟练get了分拣员的技能。
After such "devil training," teachers laugh that they have become adept at getting the sorter's skills.
行知中学每位家长间隔一米有序排队领教材。
Each parent in Hing Chi Middle School is queued up one meter apart to receive teaching materials.
为2294名学生上门送教材“上海康城”是上海市最大社区，康城学校就位于该社区内，全校有中小学生近3000名。
"Shanghai Kangcheng" is the largest community in Shanghai, with nearly 3,000 primary and middle school students in the community.
基于学生居住比较集中的特点，学校经过与康城社区党委、业委会以及校家委会共同协商，最终决定克服困难，将家长来校领取的方式，改为学校送教材上门，既最大程度节约社会资源，又能避免聚集。
Based on the characteristics of more concentrated student living, the school, after consultation with the Kangcheng Community Party Committee, the Industry Committee and the School Committee, finally decided to overcome the difficulties and change the way parents come to school to collect textbooks, so as to save social resources to the greatest extent possible and avoid aggregation.
康城学校老师和志愿者熟练打包并送教材上门。
Cambridge school teachers and volunteers skilled packaging and delivery of textbooks to the door.
方案确定后，学校募集志愿者，迅速行动。
After the programme was finalized, the school mobilized volunteers and moved quickly.
全体行政、党员、后勤人员、家长志愿者，以及康城“两委一中心”志愿者、康城小区物业志愿者多方合力，用一天半就完成了对2294个居住在康城小区学生的教材递送。
In a day and a half, all administrators, party members, logisticians, parents and volunteers, as well as volunteers from the "Two Committees One Center" in Kangcheng District, completed the delivery of 2,294 textbooks to students living in the Kangcheng district in one and a half days.
家长们收到教材后，连连感叹学校递送教材的高效，也深深为志愿者们的辛苦分送而感动。
Parents received the textbooks, even lamented the high efficiency of school delivery materials, but also deeply moved by the hard distribution of volunteers.
闵行区教育局相关负责人介绍，从2月19日起，该区启动了149所学校共计163293名中小学生教材的发放工作，保证无论在上海还是外省的学生，都能于2月28日前，人手一套纸质教材或电子版教材。
Since February 19, a total of 163,293 textbooks for primary and middle school students have been distributed in 149 schools in Min Hang District, ensuring that students, whether in Shanghai or other provinces, will have a set of printed or electronic textbooks by February 28.
本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
